    enemybullet

    game
    The class that provides the mechanics for the whole game.
    playertank
    This is the tank that the player will be controlling.
    powerup
    Defeated enemies will drop powerups at random times and the player can pick these up to gain an extra superpower.
    superpower
    Player is able to use a superpower, in which it wipes out all enemies currently on the map.
